reviewText: Very good DVD, nice to see a different area covered. Great match ups and a ton of matches. Lawler in Hawaii is different and great. Also a load of stars.

Garbage video quality.  Looks like someone just downloaded a bunch of bootleg YouTube videos and burned them to a disc.  Some of the footage is even in the wrong aspect ratio (i.e. widescreen).  Probably the worst thing I have ever bought on Amazon to date.
Cross Hawaiian, Japanese, Mainland & A Little Bit Jerry Lawler & This Is What You Have On This DVD!
